                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 10044/144.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Ambassador <persName type="to">Reid</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-04-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 18, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr Wilson quotes telegram of April 18 to the American embassy at Constantinople
                    for guidance and information of embassy at London.<note n="1" xml:id="d535fn1"
                        >Supra.</note>
                </p>
            </div>
